This is a placeholder file for the Maqder Desktop Installer.

The automatic compilation failed on the current Windows machine because creating symbolic links requires Administrator privileges or Developer Mode to be enabled.

To compile the real installer:
1. Open PowerShell or Command Prompt as Administrator.
2. Navigate to the `desktop` folder.
3. Run `npm run build:win`.

The compiled installer will be available in `desktop/dist/`. Upload that file to your server to replace this placeholder.
